    "attributes": {
        "action": "Introduce mandatory trigger warnings on fiction books",
        "additional_details": "Trigger warnings can be a simple sticker on the cover or in the introduction of a novel, stating that there is sensitive material to come.\r\n \r\nAs someone who is recovering from PTSD, I can find it deeply distressing to immerse myself in a novel and find myself reading about rape scene with no warning.",
        "background": "We would like the government to introduce mandatory trigger warnings on fiction books. This will include warnings for sexual assault, rape, and violence.",
